% PsychToolbox:PsychCal.%% help PsychToolbox % For an overview, triple-click me & hit enter.% help PsychDemos   % For demos, triple-click me & hit enter.%%   CalDataFolder       - Path to the calibration data folder "PsychCalData".%   CalibrateAmbDrvr    - Common code called by monitor calibration programs.  Script.%   CalibrateMonDrvr    - Common code called by monitor calibration programs.  Script.%   CompareMonCal       - Compare two calibration structures to see if they match.%   CheckMonCalForMachine - Check that a calibration file matches current configuration.%   ContrastMatch       - Match contrast of two gratings.%   Cross2D             - Create 2D vectors that cross combinations of passed vectors.%   Cross3D             - Create 3D vectors that cross combinations of passed vectors.%   CylToLinear         - Convert from cylindrical to linear coordinates.%   DescribeMonCal      - Print a description of calibration structure.%   DeviceToGamut       - Force device coordinates into gamut.%   DeviceToLinear      - Convert from device to linear coordinates.%   DeviceToPolar       - Convert from device to polar coordinates.%   DeviceToSettings    - Convert from device to settings coordinates.%   ExpandSettings      - Subroutine for "Acc" conversion routines.%   FindSpectralPeaks   - Find the peaks in a spectral function.%   FlushCalFile        - Remove old entries from calibration file.%   GamutToSettings     - Convert from within gamut device coordinates to settings.%   GamutToSettingsTbl  - Subroutine for GamutToSettings.%   GamutToSettingsSch  - Subroutine for GamutToSettings.%   GratingNull         - Match two luminances.%   IccProfile.mex      - Read and (soon) write ICC Profiles for monitor calibration.%   InvertGammaTable    - Subroutine for GamutToSettings.%   LinearToCyl         - Convert from linear to cylindrical coordinates.%   LinearToDevice      - Convert from linear to device coordinates.%   LinearToPolar       - Convert from linear to polar coordinates.%   LinearToSettings    - Convert from linear to settings coordinates.%   LinearToSettingsAcc - Convert from linear to settings, handle spectral shifts.%   LoadCalFile         - Load calibration data.%   MaximizeGamutContrast- Maximize contrast within gamut.%   MeasMonSpd          - Set monitor and measure spd.%   MeasMonXYZ          - Set monitor and measure XYZ.%   MeasureDpi          - Measure monitor dpi.%   PolarToDevice       - Convert from polar to device coordinates.%   PolarToLinear       - Convert from polar to linear coordinates.%   SaveCalFile         - Save calibration data.%   SearchTable         - Subroutine for GamutToSettings.%   SetColorSpace       - Set working color space for conversions.%   SetGammaMethod      - Set gamma correction method for conversions.%   SettingsToDevice    - Convert from settings to device coordinates.%   SettingsToLinear    - Convert from settings to linear coordinates.%   SettingsToLinearAcc - Convert from settings to linear, handle spectral shifts.%   SettingsToPolar     - Convert from settings to polar coordinates.%   UpdateAmbient       - Update the ambient used for conversions, in meas. units.%   UpdateAmbientLinear - Update the ambient used for conversions, in linear units.% Copyright (c) 1996-8 by Denis Pelli & David Brainard